Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An exquisite meal, Himegama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have talent as a chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had chosen the culinary arts,\Nwould the Institute have supported me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose? The Institute grants aid\Nto those with God-given gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something one can choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a calling they are assigned\Nfrom their very birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they have no need to search\Nfor meaning in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. They are truly blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do treat Chisato with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If circumstances allow it.\NI can't make any promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your skills, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let her continue\Nto stay in that place playing house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato-chan, you know this isn't a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.65,0:01:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Do you serve drinks\Nduring the day now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got you!\NMizuki's half-empty bottle, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe-san, you're on duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got another wild one today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes the Chisato special!\NWould you like one too, Kitamura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.37,0:01:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Me too!\N- Hey, over here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's one, two, three specials!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina, that's three specials!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.29,0:01:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the red, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.65,0:01:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's with all the earnings\Nfrom our clients as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you paying for ammunition\Nor transportation for jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We get funding from the DA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Technically to pay\Nfor Chisato's Lycoris activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.09,0:01:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this place is definitely losing money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because she fires\Nall those pricey bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as those parfaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you claim to be independent but\Nyou've been relying on the DA for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound just like Kusunoki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on,\NI'll handle the bookkeeping for LycoReco!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The brave choice we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Its future is being illuminated♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If we clash our selfish emotions\Nwe can't see it (yet)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫To catch up on the distance\Nwe fled from (see) let's go on a journey♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Even if we can't see the farthest lands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We just burn our lives\Nto keep living in the present♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Proof of the existence we wished for♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We kept our voices trembling\Nwhile we brandished it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫No need for regret, we go\Nhand in hand (even the dark past)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We accept it and move forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Instead of choosing an answer shown to us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫We're aspiring a new dream (always)♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Let's walk along the radiant road♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(#08 Another day, another dollar)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato. The cleaners take an\Nexorbitant fee when you call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try not to cause any damage\Nor require any restoration work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're firing too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping the fridge door open\Nwastes electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoopsie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three, seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Job done, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't been paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not paying for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we still left two wires uncut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the rest by yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:05:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see? Did you?\NI only shot once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come up with a new parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Lemme see!\NMake one for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for this time of year,\Nnow that it's getting colder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A parfait chock-full of hot fudge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morn... what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My idea for a new menu item.\NHow's it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like p...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three more orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato, for table two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order up for table three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You're doing work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did hell freeze over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato asked me to help out\Nsince we're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't in any of the pictures online!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new waitress?\NHow old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty more! Hurry up and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that disgusting grin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next party in line. Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuki, take the register!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Café LycoReco.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yamagishi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your physical!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made an appointment for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies,\NI know I said I'd come, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The café's just been so busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why,\Nbut we're selling like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not coming today, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new girl's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exercise one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitteh! Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitteh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doggo! Woof woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doggo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Handstand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doggo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chokehold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Nice choke!\N- Make sure you don't grow up to be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Trick or treat!\N- Today, we'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle it here.\NLet's split up the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do I get...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stuck running outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trick or treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Halloween!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Halloween!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Halloween!\NI'm a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a present from Takina, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato-onee-chan,\Ncan we take this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can pretend to be bankers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Me too!\N- Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it, take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep boop, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the digital revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it for cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be more useful than Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All hail the great Takina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is Takina-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kurumi.\NThey were both here just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In here?\NWhat are you two doing so sneakily?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about teaming up\Nwith Kurumi-san to make investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that going a bit too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Yamagishi-sensei)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Yamagishi-sensei?\NThis is Takina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her routine physical?\NShe can be there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my duty to make sure my men\Nare in good health as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get checked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Takina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goto-san! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Chisato-chan here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking the late shift today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there! Your order, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Chisato's uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Serving up sh-t with a smile\Nlol But the taste can't be beat!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina! Parfait's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not serving those parfaits anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?\NEveryone loves it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take care of these, Robo-Lyco.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll flush them right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! No! Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yamagishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yamagishi-sensei. This is Takina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is Chisato at the café?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I believe she should be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never came!\NAnd she won't answer my calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?\NI'll go look for her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your phone is ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Lycoris Recoil)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Takina)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if I answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Chisato?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't go to your routine physical?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!\NSomething came up, so I'll be a little late...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it on to Yamagishi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your health is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since for us,\Nour bodies serve as our capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us? Who's this "us" here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not very convincing with that gun pointed at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you alive so I can kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing! How do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that heart of yours the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how did you find out about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got Guy Hard!\NYou're into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cop, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he buddies up with McClane\Neven though they've never met...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that final scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make you some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand anything bitter.\NGot anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You spit in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that.\NI guess you don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me reminisce about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The radio tower attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,West unit, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schoolgirls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Majima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the big clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four in the coat check.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three under the register\Nin the kiosk to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've wiped them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! There's one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Majima... set off the detonator...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me sound like a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really are a freak.\NRemember now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Why would I remember you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you doing all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing means you've got some\Nsort of incredible talent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something to make people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you're doing\Nis the total opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that\Nfrom a hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not the same!\NI actually help people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you under the illusion that Alan's\Nan institute for promoting peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what everyone aside\Nfrom you has accomplished?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me the "I want to inspire the\Nworld like those gold medalists!" crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How naive can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alan's not that kind of organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,\NI made a promise to Yoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi-san... you mean an Alan operative?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in contact with Alan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of what you may know\Nthat I don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.\NYou and I really are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was selected for charity based\Non my abilities as a killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The folks at Alan are simple that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple enough to accept our murder,\Nat least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, you're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, since your partner's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until next time, radio tower Lycoris!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Majima was at your place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get him, Takina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately not. He was right there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had one of these as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell talent\Ncould he possibly have?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They support vicious criminals, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mika, you didn't hear anything\Nfrom your boyfr...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh no! What's wrong, Kurumi-chan?\N- He probably just found it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Feeling sleepy?\N- Yoshi-san would never help someone like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up my calls within three rings or less!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll decide you're in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the next hang up call will\Nsignal that I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ah, sure...\N- If you don't like it, pick up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll come find me no matter where I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, relocate to a different safe house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But that's my favorite out of all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come over to hang out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Living together?!\NWill you make me dinner again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a DA-issue gun, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I got it along with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Yoshimatsu-shi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It means a lot to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, damn it! Just stop!\NGo back to your closet and go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten colder lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The cherry blossoms were\Nin bloom when you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi-san hasn't visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from the nursery!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Doggo! So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina, you've been working\Nyour butt off lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want the café to go under.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place means a lot to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go and get your routine physical done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate it so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate it, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The needles...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of getting shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you don't blink faced with a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NYou can't dodge the needles, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The radio tower Lycoris...\Nscared of getting shots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it over with quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over? Is it? Well? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it over? Over? Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're past the hardest part!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you always act this scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's the pain, but it's\Nsticking something foreign in my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-sensei says it's just a vitamin shot,\Nbut still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Yamagishi-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to treat\Nher with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Chisato back yet?!\NIsn't she late?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you going, Takina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your fault, Mika.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The manga you brought me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫The flower you gave me\Nthat I don't know the name of♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You're not here yet today?♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫I am aware of an emotion never felt before♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Tracing along a picture decorating\Nthe window, I travel through space alone♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.43,0:23:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫That should have been enough♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫If I were to grab your hand♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.29,0:23:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫This town that knows not of solitude♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Becomes one that I can\Nnever return to ever again♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫You reached your hand out to me,\Nand a shadow is born from the light♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Sing for me to listen\Nthe continuation of this story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♫Take me to a star that I've never seen before♫
